Ex-Liverpool Owners Can’t Sue Over Sale Outside U.K.

-- B y   J a m e s   L u m l e y
-- 
2011-02-17T12:36:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/ex-liverpool-owners-can-sue-over-sale-of-club-outside-of-u-k-.html
(Corrects headline and first paragraph to indicate ex-
owners must have court permission to pursue suits outside U.K.)  Former Liverpool owners  George
Gillett  and Tom Hicks can’t sue over the forced sale of the 18-
time English soccer champion outside of the U.K. with a British
court’s permission, a London judge ruled today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
